AM\geq GM
\rm{AM} \geq \rm{GM}
 x+yz \geq 2 \sqrt{xyz}
x(1+y)+y(1+z)+z(1+x) = x+yz+y+xz+z+yx 
6
 x + y + z + xy + yz + zx \geq 6\sqrt[6]{x\cdot y\cdot z\cdot xy\cdot yz\cdot zx} = 6\sqrt[6]{x^3\cdot y^3\cdot z^3} = 6\sqrt{xyz}
\dfrac{x+y+z+xy+yz+zx}{\sqrt{xyz}} \geq 6
x = y = z = xy = yz = zx
x = y = z = 1
